summary: A new dungeon north of the Rift where refugees from the east were killed by the inhabitants of their newfound home.
descriptionHtml:
UPDATE! (v1.1)

-Fixed floating foliage in surrounding cells
-Fixed a strongbox being unobtainable in the exterior cells

A new dungeon north of the Rift where refugees from the east were killed by the inhabitants of their newfound home.

-Intended to be professional level dungeon design
-Hooked up to radiant quests
-More loot
-More to explore
-Intended for level 10 characters and higher

Please, endorse, rate, comment and enjoy!

Steam link-
http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=13808
author: Noxciss
